Jab 1.notes: Transitions to Jab 2 as early as frame 9 if it doesn't connect

Jab 2.notes: Transitions to Jab 3 as early as frame 9 if it doesn't connect

Jab 3.notes: Transitions to jab 4 as early as frame 8 if it doesn't connect

Jab 4.notes: Transitions to Jab 5 as early as frame 12 if it doesn't connect

Jab 5.notes: Transitions to Jab 6 as early as frame 14 if it doesn't connect

Jab 6.notes: Transitions to Jab 7 as early as frame 24 if it doesn't connect

Jab 7.notes: Transitions to Jab 8 as early as frame 16 if it doesn't connect

Jab 8.notes: Transitions to Jab 9 as early as frame 18 if it doesn't connect

Jab 9.notes: Transitions to Jab 10 as early as frame 17 if it doesn't connect

Flash Punch Combo (Final Hit).notes: First two hits are Jab 1 and Jab 2. Inputting the third A press on frame 10 of Jab 2 is the earliest possible that you get this. Windbox active on frames 2-6.

Down-Forward Tilt (Tsunami Kick).notes: Second number is only if you press the button again. Leg intangible on frame 8-11 and 26-28 for the axe kick. Second kick's first active frame technically ignores shields, but hits aerial oppenents only (yes, this is weird).

Back Tilt (Flash Tornado).notes: Upper body and leg intangibility on frame 7-13

Up-Back Tilt (Jump Side Kick).notes: Front leg intangible on frames 7-17, back leg on frames 7-21. Can autocancel on frame 24 to make the move +2 on shield on backward slants.

Up Tilt (Twin Pistons).notes: Second number is only if you press the button again. Upper body intangible on frame 4-10, or 4-24 if you input the second hit and arm intangibility lasts until 26.

*Crouching* Down-Forward Tilt (Tombstone.notes: Invulnerable on frame 5-14, leg and arm intangible on frame 5-19. Kazuya must be crouching for at least six frames to access this move

*Crouching* Down Tilt (Crouch Jab).notes: Lower hitbox only hits downed opponents. Arm intangible on frame 6-8. Can transition to another Crouch Jab on frame 16. Kazuya must be crouching for at least six frames to access this move.

*Crouching* Down-Back Tilt (Crouch Spin.notes: Leg intangible on frame 11-16. Kazuya must be crouching for at least six frames to access this move.

Double Dash Attack (Left Splits Kick).notes: Leg intangible on frame 7-15. Reflects on frames 7-17.

Dash Attack.notes: Legs intangible on frame 4-7. Back leg intangible on frame 13-19

Forward Smash.notes: 10.0% Damage based Armor on frame 7-24. Charge hold on frame 5.

Up Smash.notes: Arm intangible on frame 12-17. 6.0% damage based Armor on frame 7-11. Charge hold on frame 5.

Down Smash.notes: Arm intangible on frame 17-19. 6.0% damage basedArmor on frame 7-15. Charge hold on frame 2.

Demon God Fist (Uncrouching Attack).notes: Upper body intangible on frame 2-6 and arm intangible on frame 13-14. Press Neutral A within 19 frames of releasing crouch for this move to come out.

Wind God Fist.notes: Upper body intangible on frame 1-7. Arm intangible on frame 8-11. Deals .5% less damage (13%) to airborne opponents.

Electric Wind God Fist.notes: Invulnerable on frame 1-8. Intangible on 1-3 upper body, 4-8 full body, and 9-12 arm. When blocked, the opponent is forcibly pushed out of their shield, but takes no damage. Deals .5% less damage (14%) to airborne opponents.

Dragon Uppercut.notes: 5 frames of WGF/EWGF precede this move's startup. Invulnerable on frame 1-5. Upper body intangible on frame 7-11. Invulnerable on frame 12-19. Upper body intangible on frame 20-22.

Up Air.notes: Leg intangible on frame 4-9. Autoacancels on frame 30 onward

Neutral B (Devil Blaster).notes: Shieldstun is 4 on all types of lasers when not blocked at point blank range.

Devil Blaster, Air.notes: Shieldstun is 4 on all types of lasers when not blocked at point blank range.

Side B (Devil Fist).notes: Invulnerable on frame 6-9. Kazuya does not suffer hitlag from this attack, but does suffer shieldlag. Hitting a shield stops him and forces 38-45 endlag, it seems that close hits suffer less endlag.

Up B (Devil Wings).notes: Endlag can be cancelled if you land prematurely (like going up to the top battlefield platform)

Down B (Heaven's Door).notes: 10% damage based Armor on frame 5-13. 39 endlag from a successful ground slam, or 40 if you land on the same ground.
